titlealts.searchtitle: Attribute: LABOUR OR DELIVERY ONSET METHOD CODE FOR NATIONAL NEONATAL DATA SET - National Codes

stentry.p: Spontaneous (where the LABOUR OR DELIVERY ONSET METHOD is 'Spontaneous')
Induced (where the LABOUR OR DELIVERY ONSET METHOD is 'Surgical induction', 'Medical induction', or 'Combination of surgical induction and medical induction')

None (where the LABOUR OR DELIVERY ONSET METHOD is 'Caesarian section carried out before the onset of labour or a planned elective caesarian section carried out immediately following onset of labour')
